      "message": "\u003e Yeah, I thought I might need to do something like that, but was hesitant since it seems like a lot of complexity for test code when we don\u0027t expect to have sub-second precision in any tests anyways. What do you think of just always using lutimes() on MACOSX and leaving a comment about utimensat() being available in 10.13, should it ever be needed?\n\nFor test code, I think that’s perfectly acceptable.",
